.Bl -column -offset 2n \
"Kilobyte" "Prefix" "Power of 2" "Power of 10"
.It Sy Name Ta Sy Prefix Ta Sy Power of 2 Ta Sy Power of 10
.It Kilobyte Ta kB Ta 2^10 Ta 10^3
